snippet.title: Sonic Eclipse (SAGE '24 - v2.0.2 Demo) ✪ Full Playthrough (1080p/60fps)
snippet.description:
Sonic Eclipse is a 2D Classic Sonic Fan Game, created by the Brainbox Interactive Team, featured as an entry to this years (2024) Sonic Amateur Games Expo!
#sage2024 #sonicfangames #sonic2dfangames 

*Synopsis*
Looks like Eggman's up to something! But this time, things don't go as planned right from the start.
Sonic will have to team up with both friends and foes in this risky but exciting new adventure!

-

*Demo Features*
The demo here contains all acts of the first zone: Wily Weather, including a boss battle.
Main thing to keep in mind: this is not a definitive look into the game.

*DISCLAIMER*
This is also not associated with the other Sonic Eclipse or Sonic Eclipse Online.

‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒

⏱️ 𝗧𝗶𝗺𝗲𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗺𝗽𝘀
0:00 - Intro
0:15 - Title & Options

1:03 - Wily Weather Zone - Act 1
4:32 - Wily Weather Zone - Act 2
7:54 - Wily Weather Zone - Boss

9:56 - Credits
11:33 - Outro

‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒ ‒
